g that what was thencould be again.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 702, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.830483498645788, \"rank\": 0.20411784365774774, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"quite 58 years\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"hurt\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"thefeeling\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hockey was front page, back page, and top of the hour 36 years ago in 1988when Sean Kerly, Imran Sherwani, and keeper Ian Taylormade themselves household names at the SeoulOlympics.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Kerly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sean Kerly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Kerly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Kerly\"}, {\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imran_Sherwani\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imran Sherwani\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imran_Sherwani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imran_Sherwani\"}, {\"begin\": 900, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TaylorMade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taylormade\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TaylorMade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TaylorMade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hockey\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"front page\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"back page\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 819}, 