 teamhave made the podium at the last three Games - two bronzes sandwiching their famous penalty shootout gold in Rio.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9995738431674299, \"rank\": 0.00035643086996775547, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999905076038, \"rank\": 6.410340701296749e-09, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.999697066471599, \"rank\": 0.00022173610468222352, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1358, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999984452188, \"rank\": 1.5546332533114683e-09, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997875052092341, \"rank\": 0.00021253995430481183, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}],