e'?\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the meeting thinking\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a video of the Seoul 1988 team when they won gold.\", \"from\": 4841, \"to\": 4899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4864, \"end\": 4874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9982994464102548, \"rank\": 0.0010261158902895211, \"text\": \"Seoul 1988\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 4898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was their route to it, the semi-final against Australia, the final against Germany, and watching a team from Great Britain do what they did is incredibly special.\", \"from\": 4900, \"to\": 5065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4949, \"end\": 4958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.999697066471599, \"rank\": 0.00022173610468222352, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4978, \"end\": 4985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.68795264271043e-12, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5012, \"end\": 5025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999905076038, \"rank\": 6.410340701296749e-09, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wiki